text: Satellite imagery showing visits to Wuhan hospitals as well as Chinese internet search inquiries about coronavirus-type symptoms suggest the virus may have arrived in Wuhan as early as October 2019, but Chinese authorities didn't let us know. https://t.co/tj17qz4xxn https://t.co/CaoXwy0bxm
